        "jsCode": "// Loop over input items and add a new field called 'myNewField' to the JSON of each one\n//规则数组\nlet ruleArr=[13000,13001,13002,13003,13004]\nlet res=[];\nlet pcbaArr=[];\nlet others=[];\nfor (const item of $input.all()) {\n  const matNr=item.json.material_code;\n  \n  if(ruleArr.includes(Number(matNr.substring(0,5)))){\n    pcbaArr.push(item.json);\n  }else{\n    others.push(item.json);\n  }\n}\nres.push({pcbaArr})\nres.push({others})\nreturn res;"
      },
